@startuml
' 小说模式时序图
title 小说模式时序图
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor black
    ArrowFontColor black
    ActorBorderColor black
    ActorBackgroundColor white
    ActorFontColor black
    ParticipantBorderColor black
    ParticipantBackgroundColor white
    ParticipantFontColor black
    LifeLineBorderColor black
    LifeLineBackgroundColor white
    DividerBorderColor none
    DividerBackgroundColor transparent
    DividerFontColor black
    DividerFontStyle normal  ' 取消加粗，普通字体
}
' 定义参与者（从左至右，与SVG顺序一致）
actor "用户" as User
participant "前端" as Frontend
participant "后端" as Backend
participant "MySQL" as DB
participant "高德地图API" as Gaode
participant "DeepSeekAPI" as AI

' ========== 开始小说导航 ==========
User -> Frontend : 开始小说导航
activate Frontend

Frontend -> Backend : POST /api/startNavigationNoBook\n(起点, 终点, 通行方式)
activate Backend

Backend -> Gaode : 请求驾驶路线
activate Gaode
Gaode --> Backend : 返回路线信息
deactivate Gaode

Backend --> Frontend : 返回轨迹ID
deactivate Backend
Frontend --> User : 显示导航路线
deactivate Frontend

' ========== 获取章节内容 ==========
User -> Frontend : 获取章节内容
activate Frontend

Frontend -> Backend : POST /api/get-chapter\n(bookId, trajectoryId, length)
activate Backend

Backend -> DB : 查询book表
activate DB
DB --> Backend : 返回书籍信息
deactivate DB

Backend -> DB : 查询area表
activate DB
DB --> Backend : 返回区域信息
deactivate DB

Backend -> AI : 生成章节内容
activate AI
AI --> Backend : 返回章节文本
deactivate AI

Backend -> DB : 插入章节数据到chapter表
activate DB
DB --> Backend : 确认保存成功
deactivate DB

Backend --> Frontend : 返回章节文本
deactivate Backend

Frontend -> User : 播放章节语音
User --> Frontend : 收听章节内容
deactivate Frontend

@enduml